'''Inezggan''' d yiwen iɣrem deg tama n iɣrem n [[Agadir|Ugadir]] (12 km) i yellan di tasga n [[Sus|Sus-Mast-Drεa]] . '''Inezggan''' d almuggar (ssuq) n tsbbabt imqqeranen deg tasga-ya. Yiwen deg ilmuggarn lli baḥra ittwattas ufgan amaziɣ iɣ ira ad isaɣ kra n tɣawsa. [[Tasbbabt|Tasbbabt]] tella s tbḍit {{wp/shi/Tafransist| détailles}} wala s ugudi. Zedɣen deg-s uggar n 112 753 n imezdaɣ s uṭṭunen n 2004.
 
Yiwen wass n [[wp/shi/Ussan|asinas]] neɣ Tlaṭ ass amqqran n ssuq. Maca ammussu n tsbbabt illa bdda deg Inezggan azal ar tuẓẓumin n ḍi yid. 

==Tasbbabt==
Ilmuggaren lli deg-s illa :

:*Almuggar n [[wp/shi/Ussan|ṭlaṭa]] ( imalas f imalas )
:*Almuggar ameqqran n lxeḍrt (ass f wass)
:*Almuggar ameẓyan (Marché) (ass f wass)
:*Almuggar n imkraḍ (ass f wass)

==Aksimen==

Iksimen d yiwet n taqbilt tamzwarut lli iskaren (i yeggan) almuggar deg uzaɣar n '''Inezggan'''.

